name: Sona Buvelle (League of Legends)
description:
LoRa trained on Sona Buvelle from League of Legends.

Triggers with Sona \(league of legends\), blue hair, blue eyes, gradient hair, sometimes it is better to add long hair and collarbone, then you can play with poses, clothing, or other LoRas.

Known issues:

  • Sometimes it forces parts of her dress into other outfits, a workaround is to get your desired outfit (inside brackets) and dress into negative prompts.

  • Sometimes it can generate twins or multiple views, for this add multiple girls, multiple views in negative prompts.
